data.description: This home will not last long! Excellent price in a great location. This split level home is situated on a pristine lot with lots of room for play and entertaining. Trex composite decking on the newly remodeled deck overlooks the ample back yard with a relaxing view of the wooded treeline. This is a well maintained home that featrues an eat-in kitchen, stained cabinets, tiled backsplash and tiled floors. The spacious livingroom boasts a cozy stone fireplace, LVP flooring and lots of natural light. The lovely rocking chair front porch overlooks a luciously green lawn. The nighborhood is small and quaint. A must see!
